node.text:
Would you dare to pass through this Via Ferrata? 😳 

The new Via Ferrata Delle Aquile, on the top of Paganella, is a highly emotional and spectacular via ferrata that gives you unforgettable emotions; the sight embraces whole Trentino, but keeping fixed on the track too.

Recommendation:
Avoid the queue: purchase online your ticket and go directly to turnstile. Choose the stage and pay with your credit card. You will receive by email your ticket (you can print the ticket or save it in your smartphone), scan it on the orange scanner on the turnstile located at the gates of the lift.

Video by: @niklaskoessel 
Location: Trentino, Italy 🇮🇹

node.text:
Have you been to Canada? Here are some beautiful places to visit if you haven't visited. 🇨🇦
Photos by: @mthiessen 
Locations in Canada: ⬇️
1-3. Niagara Falls, Ontario
4. Spirit Island, Alberta
5. Jasper, Alberta
6. Golden fields near Stony Plain, Alberta
7. Emerald Lake, British Columbia
8. Moraine Lake Road, Alberta
9. Lake Louise, Alberta
10. Edmonton, Alberta

If you've been to any of these let us know in the comments below! 🇨🇦

node.text:
One of Australia's finest waterfront residences with a guide of AUD $20,000,000 plus - Known as Mandalay House located in Airlie Beach, Queensland. 

The Mediterranean inspired residence took 3.5 years to construct with no cost spared in its creation. The home rests on a private 4,242sqm with a palatial 2,649sqm of living and entertaining, pool and marina. Marble finishes, high ceilings, exquisite joinery, expansive living and sitting areas, banquet sized dining. Games room plus home theatre with tiered seating, projector, screen and sound, gymnasium, ducted a/c. Six further king-sized bedrooms with ensuite and sitting, car accommodation for five, lift access. 
Via: @darrencurtis_christies
